General.Name: Samhällsbyggnadsbolaget i Norden AB (publ)
General.Description: Samhällsbyggnadsbolaget i Norden AB (publ) owns, develops, and manages residential and social infrastructure properties in the Nordic region. It operates through three segments: Residential Properties, Community Service Properties, and Other Properties. The Residential Properties segment primarily consists of apartments and townhouses. The Community Service Properties segment includes schools, retirement homes, housing for the disabled, and properties operated by municipal and governmental agencies/authorities. The Other Properties segment operates commercial properties. Samhällsbyggnadsbolaget i Norden AB (publ) was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
